| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0920 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 35bb8902-9f0d-5066-997d-cb494a65a330"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
